## 2026-07-22 — workflow sequencing fix

- Finding: phase00 compression previously ran concurrently with the next business phase, so downstream input could race the summary index.
- Fix: await phase00 immediately after each completed business phase (1 through 7) before the following phase begins. Phase 8 is terminal archival/prediction work and has no downstream consumer or phase00 source payload.

